## CORE VISUAL PRINCIPLES (svi benchmark sajtovi)

### 1. HERO STANDARD

Na osnovu Clay, Instrument, DD.NYC, Huemor:

**Mora imati:**
- Instant visual impact (< 0.5s do utiska)
- Clear hierarchy: hero title → subtitle → CTA
- Premium typography (minimum 48px desktop hero)
- Micro-animations na load (subtle, sophisticated)
- Clear value proposition bez generičkih fraza

**Layout pattern:**
```
[Large statement text 60-120px]
[Supporting line 18-24px, lighter weight]
[Primary CTA] [Secondary action]
```

**Animacije:**
- Fade in + slight upward movement (20-40px)
- Stagger timing između elemenata (100-200ms delay)
- Easing: ease-out ili custom cubic-bezier
- Total animation time: 0.6s - 1.2s

### 2. SECTION TRANSITIONS

Standard iz Huemor, Instrument, 500designs:

**Scroll-triggered reveals:**
- IntersectionObserver sa threshold 0.1-0.3
- Fade + translate (ne samo fade)
- Stagger children animations
- Respect prefers-reduced-motion

**CSS standard:**
```css
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(40px);
  transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;
}

.reveal.active {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}
```

### 3. TYPOGRAPHY HIERARCHY

Standard iz svih benchmark sajtova:

**Desktop:**
- Hero: 60-120px
- H1: 48-72px
- H2: 36-48px
- H3: 24-32px
- Body: 16-20px
- Small: 14-16px

**Mobile scale down:**
- Hero: 36-56px
- H1: 32-40px
- H2: 24-32px
- Body: 16-18px

**Font weights:**
- Display/Hero: 500-700
- Headings: 500-600
- Body: 400
- Captions: 400-500

**Line height:**
- Headings: 1.1 - 1.3
- Body: 1.5 - 1.7

### 4. SPACING SYSTEM

Standard iz DD.NYC, Clay, 500designs:

```css
--space-xs: 8px;
--space-sm: 16px;
--space-md: 24px;
--space-lg: 40px;
--space-xl: 64px;
--space-2xl: 96px;
--space-3xl: 128px;

--section-padding-mobile: 60px 20px;
--section-padding-desktop: 120px 40px;
```

**Minimum section padding:**
- Desktop: 100-140px vertical
- Mobile: 60-80px vertical

### 5. HOVER & INTERACTION STATES

Standard iz svih premium sajtova:

**Buttons:**
```css
.btn {
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

.btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}
```

**Cards:**
- Hover lift: 4-8px
- Shadow enhancement
- Optional border color shift
- Scale: 1.02 - 1.05 (optional, subtle)

**Links:**
- Underline animation (left to right ili center out)
- Color transition
- Subtle weight change (optional)

### 6. SCROLL PROGRESS & FEEDBACK

Standard iz Instrument, Huemor, DD.NYC:

**Mora imati:**
- Smooth scroll behavior
- Progress indicator (optional ali poželjno)
- Section-based navigation highlights
- Subtle parallax ili depth changes through scroll

**Ne preopterećivati:**
- Scroll hijacking je zabranjen
- Native scroll behavior mora ostati prirodan
- Accessibility mora biti očuvana

### 7. GRID & LAYOUT SYSTEM

Standard iz Clay, 500designs, BopDesign:

**Desktop grid:**
- 12-column system
- Max-width: 1200-1440px
- Gutter: 24-40px
- Margins: 40-80px

**Mobile:**
- Single column sa card/tile breakpoints
- Gutter: 16-24px
- Margins: 20-24px

**Layout patterns:**
- Asymmetric layouts za visual interest
- Text-image splits (60/40 ili 50/50)
- Full-bleed sections alternating sa constrained content

