## INTERACTION PATTERNS (direktno sa benchmark sajtova)

### Clay-style Transitions

**Section reveals:**
- Fade up sa opacity
- Element staggering
- Smooth bezier curves
- Respect scroll speed

### Instrument-style Fluidity

**Characteristics:**
- Very smooth transitions (0.6s - 1s)
- Subtle scale changes
- Refined easing functions
- Elegant state changes

### Huemor-style Depth

**Layer system:**
- Background, midground, foreground
- Different scroll speeds
- 3D transform space setup
- Proper z-index hierarchy

### DD.NYC-style Magnetic Effects

**Cursor interaction:**
- Elements follow cursor within bounds
- Magnetic pull on hover
- Smooth tracking with damping
- Works on hero elements, cards, CTAs

