## ANIMATION PERFORMANCE STANDARDS

Svi benchmark sajtovi drže visoke performance standarde:

**Obavezno:**
- 60fps minimum
- GPU-accelerated properties only (transform, opacity)
- Avoid layout thrashing
- Use will-change sparingly
- RequestAnimationFrame za JS animations

**Zabranjeno:**
- Animating width, height, top, left directly
- Heavy animations on mobile without testing
- Scroll listeners without throttle/debounce
- Simultaneous animations of 50+ elements

**Optimizacija:**
```css
.animated-element {
  will-change: transform, opacity;
  transform: translateZ(0); /* Force GPU layer */
}
```

