Standard iz Clay, 500designs, Instrument:

**Grid patterns:**
- Masonry ili bento grid
- Alternating sizes
- Featured vs standard entries
- Clear hover states

**Info hierarchy na card:**
```
[Visual / Thumbnail]
[Project Title]
[Brief descriptor]
[Tags/Categories]
[Link/CTA]
```

**Hover reveal:**
- Overlay sa dodatnim info
- Image zoom ili shift
