## COLOR & VISUAL ATMOSPHERE

Standard iz svih benchmark sajtova:

**Background treatment:**
- Solid color blocks alternating
- Subtle gradients (ne preterano)
- Texture overlays (grain, noise - subtle)
- Depth kroz color contrast

**Accent usage:**
- 1 primary accent color
- Optional secondary accent
- Used sparingly za CTAs, highlights, hover states
- Consistent throughout site

**Shadows & depth:**
```css
--shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
--shadow-md: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
--shadow-lg: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
--shadow-xl: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
```

---

## RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR

Standard iz BopDesign, Storm Brain, Creative Momentum:

**Breakpoints:**
```css
--mobile: 375px;
--tablet: 768px;
--desktop: 1024px;
--wide: 1440px;
```

**Mobile-specific:**
- Touch-friendly tap targets (min 44x44px)
- Simplified animations (redukovani ili isključeni parallax)
- Optimized image loading
- Hamburger menu mora biti premium quality
- Swipe gestures gde ima smisla

**Performance targets:**
- Mobile Lighthouse score: 90+
- Desktop Lighthouse score: 95+
- First Contentful Paint: < 1.5s
- Time to Interactive: < 3s

---

## NAVIGATION STANDARDS

Standard iz Clay, Instrument, DD.NYC:

**Desktop nav:**
- Clean, minimal
- Fixed ili hide on scroll down / reveal on scroll up
- Smooth background transition na scroll
- Premium hover states
- Clear active state

**Mobile nav:**
- Full-screen overlay ili slide-in panel
- Large, tappable items
- Smooth open/close animation (0.3-0.5s)
- Close button jasno vidljiv
- Optional blur ili dim background

---

## CTA STANDARDS

Standard iz svih benchmark sajtova:

**Primary CTA:**
- Visually dominant
- Clear, action-oriented text
- Strong hover state
- Consistent positioning
- Adequate size (min 48px height)

**Button styles (primeri):**
```css
/* Solid primary */
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: white;
  padding: 16px 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 500;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

/* Outline secondary */
.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px solid var(--border);
  padding: 14px 30px;
}
```

**States:**
- Default → Hover (lift, shadow, color shift)
- Active (scale down)
- Disabled (reduced opacity, no interaction)

