## CONTENT PRESENTATION PATTERNS

### Text Blocks (Clay, Instrument standard)

**Principles:**
- Max-width 700px za body text
- Clear paragraph spacing (1.5-2em)
- Subheadings break up content
- Pull quotes ili highlights za emphasis
- Ne predugi pasusi (3-5 lines max)

### Image Treatment (DD.NYC, 500designs standard)

**Principles:**
- High quality images only (no pixelation)
- Consistent aspect ratios
- Lazy loading after first viewport
- WebP format sa fallback
- Alt text obavezan

### Video Integration (Instrument, Creative Momentum standard)

**Principles:**
- Autoplay background video: muted, loop, no controls
- Featured video: controls, quality options
- Poster frame za pre-load
- Lazy load video sources
- Mobile: reduce quality ili show poster only

---

## FOOTER STANDARDS

Standard iz Storm Brain, BopDesign, Clay:

**Mora sadržati:**
- Contact info
- Navigation links
- Social links
- Legal links (privacy, terms)
- Optional newsletter signup

**Design standard:**
- Clear hierarchy
- Premium spacing
- Subtle separation od main content
- Clean, readable layout
- Not an afterthought - well designed

---

## LOADING & PERFORMANCE

Standard iz svih premium sajtova:

**Loading states:**
- Premium loader ili skeleton screens
- No generic spinners unless styled premium
- Progressive content reveal
- Smooth transition from load to ready

**Optimization obavezno:**
- Image optimization (WebP, srcset, lazy load)
- Font loading strategy (swap ili optional)
- Critical CSS inline
- Deferred non-critical JS
- Resource hints (preconnect, prefetch)

---

## ACCESSIBILITY BASELINE

Standard iz svih profesionalnih sajtova:

**Minimum requirements:**
- Semantic HTML
- ARIA labels gde potrebno
- Keyboard navigation support
- Focus states clearly visible
- Color contrast WCAG AA minimum
- Alt text na images
- Skip links za navigation
- Respect prefers-reduced-motion

---

## QUALITY FILTERS

Pre nego što se bilo šta smatra završenim:

### Visual Quality Check:
- Da li deluje kao premium studio website?
- Da li bi ovo moglo biti u Awwwards showcase?
- Da li interaction quality parira best-in-class primeru?
- Da li je mobile iskustvo isto tako premium?

### Technical Quality Check:
- Performance score 90+ na Lighthouse?
- Sve animations smooth 60fps?
- Accessibility errors: 0
- Console errors: 0
- Responsive breakpoints: tested and working?

### Brand Quality Check:
- Da li održava brand identity?
- Da li deluje kao isto autor kao prethodna sekcija?
- Da li copy zvuči profesionalno?
- Da li je CTA jasan i jak?

---

## KONKRETAN RADNI STANDARD

Kada radiš na bilo kom vizuelnom ili interaktivnom delu:

**Pitaj:**
1. Kako bi ovo uradio Clay?
2. Kako bi ovo uradio Huemor sa svojim layer systemom?
3. Kako bi DD.NYC dodao cursor interaction?
4. Da li ovo parira top 1% globalnih studio websitova?

**Ako odgovor na #4 nije "da", preradi.**

**Ne prihvataj:**
- "Dovoljno dobro"
- "Prolazi"
- "Može bolje ali ok"

**Prihvataj samo:**
- "Ovo je premium"
- "Ovo konkuriše najboljima"
- "Ovo je benchmark quality"

---

## FINALNA PROVERA

Pre završetka bilo koje sekcije ili feature-a:

- [ ] Visual quality: top 5% global studio standard?
- [ ] Interaction quality: smooth, premium, thoughtful?
- [ ] Performance: 60fps, optimized, fast load?
- [ ] Mobile: premium experience maintained?
- [ ] Accessibility: baseline standards met?
- [ ] Brand consistency: feels like same author?
- [ ] Copy quality: professional, clear, strong?
- [ ] Technical: clean code, maintainable?

**Ako ma koja stavka nije ✓, onda nije gotovo.**

